== Failure Modes and Mitigations ==

* '''Stale ephemeris.''' → Cached ephemeris refreshed at least daily; staleness > 24 h forces standby.
* '''Wrong-chart loading.''' → MCU-B verified-boot binding; chart change requires physical re-flash.
* '''Stabilizer offline → Harmonizer alone.''' → Auto-disengage interlock; Harmonizer will not operate without a live Stabilizer baseline.
* '''Operator over-reliance.''' → Default dwell windows; mandatory off-cycles each hour.
* '''[[SynastryEngine]] compromise.''' → MCU-B independent envelope cap; signed target tuples; rejected unsigned tuples log + drop.
* '''Driving an unstable operator further.''' → Stabilizer interlock; rate-limit on target gradient.

